node.text: story time: i skated to this song for the first time in a long time and actually cried so hard (wait til end… nobody else??) and in that very moment, a lil young lady dressed in the perfect shiny blue skate dress approached me to say hi. i didn’t explain why i was wiping tears from my cheeks, but as her mom snapped a pic. of us, grinning ear to ear, i think it will be clear 🥲 they are happy tears
